txt.en: 'Mmm, where's the beer?'\n\nWhat a disgrace. You should make sure Agmund gets out of sight before the Elves start getting offended by his public display of drunkenness.
Designated Escort: A Disturbance in Duillond
A member of the Ale Association seems to have landed drunk in Duillond, where all the Elves can see him. Shameful!
Now Agmund can sleep it off without embarrassing his neighbours
You left Agmund to make a fool of himself
At least he is out of sight now.
Agmund is the disgrace of Duillond.\n\nYou should escort the drunken dwarf to a secluded place where he won't be disturbing the good-mannered Elves around town.
Escort the drunken dwarf out of this public place
